Our Morocco Beard Oil is an adventurous blend of exotic oils and spices — peppermint, cloves, vanilla, coffee, and precious resins. Upon applying the beard oil you immediately find yourself walking through a Moroccan market surrounded by exotic scents and sights — ready for whatever adventure might present itself.  For a true man of the world, Morocco will have you daydreaming endlessly of spontaneous adventures to faraway places.

Beard Oil with Argan Oil

  • Natural oils keep facial hair soft and reduce itchiness associated with beard growth
  • Exotic and inviting scent
  • Includes shaker insert to make dispensing easy
